[
    {
        "source_sentence": "百喻經卷第一",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543a04_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "尊者僧伽斯那撰",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543a06_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "蕭齊天竺三藏求那毘地譯",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543a07_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "愚人食鹽喻　愚人集牛乳喻　以梨打破頭喻　婦詐語稱死喻　渴見水喻　子死欲停置家中喻　認人為兄喻　山羗偷官庫喻　歎父德行喻　三重樓喻　婆羅門殺子喻　煮黑石蜜漿喻　說人喜瞋喻　殺商主祀天喻　醫與王女藥令卒長大喻　灌甘蔗喻　債半錢喻　就樓磨刀喻　乘船失釪喻　人說王縱暴喻　婦女欲更求子喻1 愚人食鹽喻（一）愚人食鹽喻昔有愚人至於他家，主人與食嫌淡無味，主人聞已更為益鹽。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543a18_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "既得鹽美，便自念言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543a19_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「所以美者緣有鹽故，少有尚爾況復多也？",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543a20_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」愚人無智便空食鹽，食已口爽返為其患。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543a21_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬彼外道聞節飲食可以得道，即便斷食或經七日或十五日，徒自困餓無益於道。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543a23_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如彼愚人，以鹽美故而空食之，致令口爽，此亦復爾。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543a24_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "2 愚人集牛乳喻（二）愚人集牛乳喻昔有愚人將會賓客，欲集牛乳以擬供設，而作是念：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543a27_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我今若豫於日日中𤚲取牛乳，牛乳漸多卒無安處，或復酢敗。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543a28_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不如即就牛腹盛之，待臨會時當頓𤚲取。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543a29_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」作是念已，便捉牸牛母子，各繫異處。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543b01_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "却後一月，爾乃設會迎置賓客，方牽牛來欲𤛓取乳，而此牛乳即乾無有。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543b03_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時為眾賓或瞋或笑。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543b04_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "愚人亦爾，欲修布施，方言待我大有之時，然後頓施。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543b05_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "未及聚頃，或為縣官水火盜賊之所侵奪，或卒命終不及時施，彼亦如是。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543b07_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "3 以梨打頭破喻（三）以梨打頭破喻昔有愚人頭上無毛，時有一人以梨打頭，乃至二三悉皆傷破，時此愚人默然忍受不知避去。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543b11_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "傍人見已而語之言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543b11_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「何不避去，乃住受打致使頭破？",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543b12_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」愚人答言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543b12_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如彼人者憍慢恃力癡無智慧，見我頭上無有髮毛謂為是石，以梨打我頭破乃爾。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543b14_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」傍人語言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543b14_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝自愚癡，云何名彼以為癡也？",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543b15_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝若不癡，為他所打，乃至頭破不知逃避？",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543b16_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」比丘亦爾，不能具修信、戒、聞、慧，但整威儀以招利養，如彼愚人被他打頭不知避去，乃至傷破反謂他癡，此比丘者亦復如是。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543b19_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "4 婦詐稱死喻（四）婦詐稱死喻昔有愚人，其婦端正，情甚愛重；",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543b21_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "婦無直信，後於中間共他交往，邪婬心盛欲逐傍夫捨離己婿，於是密語一老母言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543b23_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我去之後，汝可齎一死婦女屍安著屋中，語我夫言，云我已死。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543b25_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」老母於後伺其夫主不在之時，以一死屍置其家中。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543b26_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "及其夫還，老母語言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543b27_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝婦已死。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543b27_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」夫即往視，信是己婦，哀哭懊惱，大𧂐薪油燒取其骨，以囊盛之晝夜懷挾。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543b29_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "婦於後時心厭傍夫便還歸家，語其夫言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543c01_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我是汝妻。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543c01_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」夫答之言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543c01_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我婦久死，汝是阿誰妄言我婦？",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543c02_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」乃至二三猶故不信。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543c02_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如彼外道聞他邪說心生惑著，謂為真實永不可改，雖聞正教不信受持。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543c04_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "5 渴見水喻（五）渴見水喻過去有人，癡無智慧，極渴須水，見熱時炎謂為是水，即便逐走至辛頭河，既至河所對視不飲。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543c08_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "傍人語言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543c08_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝患渴逐水，今至水所何故不飲？",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543c09_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」愚人答言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543c09_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「君可飲盡，我當飲之，此水極多俱不可盡，是故不飲。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543c10_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時眾人聞其此語，皆大嗤笑。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543c11_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如外道僻取其理，以己不能具持佛戒，遂便不受，致使將來無得道分、流轉生死，若彼愚人見水不飲為時所笑，亦復如是。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543c14_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "6 子死欲停置家中喻（六）子死欲停置家中喻昔有愚人養育七子，一子先死。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543c16_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時此愚人見子既死，便欲停置於其家中，自欲棄去。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543c17_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "傍人見已而語之言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543c18_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「生死道異，當速莊嚴致於遠處而殯葬之，云何得留自欲棄去？",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543c19_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時愚人聞此語已即自思念：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543c20_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「若不得留要當葬者，須更殺一子停擔兩頭乃可勝致。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543c22_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」於是便更殺其一子，而擔負之遠葬林野。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543c23_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時人見之，深生嗤笑怪未曾有。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543c23_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如比丘私犯一戒，情憚改悔，默然覆藏自說清淨，或有知者即語之言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543c25_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「出家之人守持禁戒如護明珠不使缺落，汝今云何違犯所受欲不懺悔？",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543c27_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」犯戒者言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543c27_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「苟須懺者，更就犯之然後當出。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543c28_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」遂便破戒多作不善，爾乃頓出。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0543c29_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如彼愚人一子既死又殺一子，今此比丘亦復如是。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544a01_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "7 認人為兄喻（七）認人為兄喻昔有一人形容端正智慧具足，復多錢財，舉世人聞無不稱歎。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544a04_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時有愚人見其如此，便言我兄。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544a05_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所以爾者，彼有錢財須者則用之，是故為兄；",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544a06_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "見其還債，言非我兄。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544a06_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "傍人語言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544a07_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝是愚人！",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544a07_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何須財名他為兄？",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544a07_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "及其債時復言非兄。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544a08_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」愚人答言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544a08_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我以欲得彼之錢財認之為兄，實非是兄，若其債時則稱非兄。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544a10_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」人聞此語無不笑之。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544a10_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "猶彼外道，聞佛善語貪竊而用以為己有，乃至傍人教使修行不肯修行，而作是言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544a12_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「為利養故，取彼佛語化道眾生，而無實事，云何修行？",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544a14_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」猶向愚人為得財故言是我兄，及其債時復言非兄，此亦如是。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544a15_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "8 山羌偷官庫喻（八）山羗偷官庫喻過去之世有一山羗，偷王庫物而遠逃走。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544a17_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時國王遣人四出推尋捕得，將至王邊。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544a18_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "王即責其所得衣處，山羗答言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544a19_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我衣乃是祖父之物。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544a20_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」王遣著衣，實非山羗本所有故，不知著之，應在手者著於脚上，應在腰者返著頭上。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544a22_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "王見賊已，集諸臣等共詳此事，而語之言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544a23_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「若是汝之祖父已來所有衣者，應當解著，云何顛倒用上為下？",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544a24_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以不解故，定知汝衣必是偷得，非汝舊物。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544a25_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」借以為譬，王者如佛，寶藏如法，愚癡羗者猶如外道，竊聽佛法著已法中以為自有，然不解故，布置佛法迷亂上下，不知法相。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544a28_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如彼山羗得王寶衣，不識次第顛倒而著，亦復如是。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544a29_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "9 歎父德行喻（九）歎父德行喻昔時有人於眾人中，歎己父德而作是言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544b02_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我父慈仁不害不盜，直作實語兼行布施。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544b03_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」時有愚人聞其此語便作是念言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544b04_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我父德行復過汝父。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544b05_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」諸人問言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544b05_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「有何德行請道其事？",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544b06_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」愚人答曰：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544b06_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我父小來斷絕婬欲初無染污。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544b07_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」眾人語言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544b07_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「若斷婬欲，云何生汝？",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544b07_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」深為時人之所怪笑。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544b08_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "猶如世間無智之流，欲讚人德不識其實，反致毀呰，如彼愚者，意好歎父言成過失，此亦如是。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544b10_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "10 三重樓喻（一〇）三重樓喻往昔之世，有富愚人癡無所知，到餘富家見三重樓，高廣嚴麗軒敞踈朗，心生渴仰即作是念：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544b14_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我有財錢不減於彼，云何頃來而不造作如是之樓？",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544b15_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」即喚木匠而問言曰：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544b15_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「解作彼家端正舍不？",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544b16_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」木匠答言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544b16_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「是我所作。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544b17_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」即便語言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544b17_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「今可為我造樓如彼。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544b17_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」是時木匠即便經地壘墼作樓。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544b18_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "愚人見其壘墼作舍，猶懷疑惑不能了知，而問之言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544b19_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「欲作何等？",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544b20_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」木匠答言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544b20_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「作三重屋。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544b20_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」愚人復言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544b20_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我不欲下二重之屋，先可為我作最上屋。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544b21_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」木匠答言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544b22_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「無有是事，何有不作最下重屋而得造彼第二之屋？",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544b23_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不造第二云何得造第三重屋？",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544b24_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」愚人固言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544b24_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我今不用下二重屋，必可為我作最上者。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544b25_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」時人聞已便生怪笑，咸作此言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544b26_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「何有不造下第一屋而得上者？",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544b26_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」譬如世尊四輩弟子，不能精勤修敬三寶，󰝬惰懈怠欲求道果，而作是言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544b28_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我今不用餘下三果，唯求得彼阿羅漢果。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544b29_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」亦為時人之所嗤笑，如彼愚者等無有異。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544c01_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "11 婆羅門殺子喻（一一）婆羅門殺子喻昔有婆羅門自謂多知，於諸星術種種技藝無不明達，恃己如此，欲顯其德，遂至他國，抱兒而哭。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544c05_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有人問婆羅門言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544c05_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝何故哭？",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544c06_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」婆羅門言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544c06_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「今此小兒七日當死，愍其夭傷以是哭耳。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544c07_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」時人語言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544c07_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「人命難知，計算喜錯，設七日頭或能不死，何為豫哭？",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544c08_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」婆羅門言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544c09_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「日月可闇星宿可落，我之所記終無違失。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544c10_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」為名利故，至七日頭自殺其子以證己說。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544c11_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時諸世人却後七日聞其兒死，咸皆歎言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544c12_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「真是智者，所言不錯。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544c12_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」心生信服悉來致敬。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544c13_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "猶如佛之四輩弟子為利養故自稱得道，有愚人法殺善男子詐現慈德，故使將來受苦無窮，如婆羅門為驗己言殺子惑世。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544c16_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "12 煮黑石蜜漿喻（一二）煮黑石蜜漿喻昔有愚人煮黑石蜜，有一富人來至其家。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544c18_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時此愚人便作是念：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544c19_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我今當取黑石蜜漿與此富人。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544c20_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」即著少水用置火中。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544c20_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "即於火上以扇扇之望得使冷。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544c21_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "傍人語言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544c21_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「下不止火，扇之不已云何得冷？",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544c22_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時人眾悉皆嗤笑。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544c22_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其猶外道不滅煩惱熾然之火，少作苦行臥蕀刺上，五熱炙身而望清涼寂靜之道，終無是處，徒為智者之所怪笑，受苦現在殃流來劫。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544c26_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "13 說人喜瞋喻（一三）說人喜瞋喻過去有人，共多人眾坐於屋中，歎一外人德行極好，唯有二過：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0544c29_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者喜瞋，二者作事倉卒。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545a01_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時此人過在門外，聞作是語便生瞋恚，即入其屋擒彼道己愚惡之人，以手打撲。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545a03_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "傍人問言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545a03_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「何故打也？",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545a03_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」其人答言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545a03_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我曾何時喜瞋、倉卒？",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545a04_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而此人者道：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545a04_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『我順喜瞋恚，作事倉卒。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545a05_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』是故打之。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545a05_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」傍人語言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545a05_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝今喜瞋倉卒之相即時現驗，云何諱之？",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545a06_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」人說過惡而起怨責，深為眾人怪其愚惑。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545a07_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如世間飲酒之夫，躭荒沈酒作諸放逸，見人呵責返生尤疾，苦引證作用自明白，若此愚人諱聞己過，見他道說返欲打撲之。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545a10_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "14 殺商主祀天喻（一四）殺商主祀天喻昔有賈客欲入大海，入大海之法要須導師然後可去，即共求覓得一導師，既得之已相將發引至曠野中。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545a14_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有一天祠當須人祀然後得過，於是眾賈共思量言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545a15_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我等伴黨盡是親親如何可殺？",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545a16_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "唯此導師中用祀天。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545a17_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」即殺導師以用祭祀。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545a17_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "祀天已竟，迷失道路不知所趣，窮困死盡。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545a18_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一切世人亦復如是，欲入法海取其珍寶，當修善法行以為導師。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545a20_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "毀破善行，生死曠路永無出期，經歷三塗受苦長遠，如彼商賈，將入大海，殺其導者，迷失津濟，終致困死。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545a22_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "15 醫與王女藥令卒長大喻（一五）醫與王女藥令卒長大喻昔有國王產生一女，喚醫語言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545a24_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「為我與藥立使長大。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545a25_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」醫師答言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545a25_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我與良藥能使即大，但今卒無，方須求索。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545a26_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比得藥頃，王要莫看，待與藥已然後示王。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545a27_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」於是即便遠方取藥經十二年，得藥來還與女令服，將示於王，王見歡喜即自念言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545a29_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「實是良醫，與我女藥能令卒長。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545b01_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」便勅左右賜以珍寶。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545b01_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時諸人等笑王無智，不曉籌量生來年月，見其長大，謂是藥力。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545b03_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世人亦爾，詣善知識而啟之言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545b03_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我欲求道願見教授，使我立得。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545b04_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」善知識師以方便故，教令坐禪觀十二緣起，漸積眾德獲阿羅漢，倍踊躍歡喜而作是言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545b06_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「快哉大師！",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545b07_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "速能令我證最妙法。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545b07_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」16 灌甘蔗喻（一六）灌甘蔗喻昔有二人共種甘蔗，而作誓言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545b09_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「種好者賞，其不好者當重罰之。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545b10_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」時二人中，一者念言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545b11_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「甘蔗極甜，若壓取汁還灌甘蔗樹，甘美必甚，得勝於彼。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545b12_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」即壓甘蔗取汁用溉，冀望滋味返敗種子，所有甘蔗一切都失。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545b13_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世人亦爾，欲求善福，恃己豪貴專形俠勢，迫脅下民陵奪財物，用作福本期善果，不知將來反獲其患殃，如壓甘蔗彼此都失。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545b16_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "17 債半錢喻（一七）債半錢喻往有商人貸他半錢久不得償，即便往債。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545b18_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "前有大河，雇他兩錢然後得渡，到彼往債竟不得見，來還渡河復雇兩錢。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545b20_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "為半錢債而失四錢，兼有道路疲勞乏困，所債甚少所失極多，果被眾人之所怪笑。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545b22_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世人亦爾，要少名利致毀大行，苟容己身不顧禮義，現受惡名後得苦報。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545b24_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "18 就樓磨刀喻（一八）就樓磨刀喻昔有一人，貧窮困苦為王作事，日月經久身體羸瘦。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545b27_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "王見憐愍，賜一死駝。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545b27_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "貧人得已即便剝皮，嫌刀鈍故求石欲磨，乃於樓上得一磨石，磨刀令利來下而剝。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545b29_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是數數往來磨刀，後轉勞苦憚不能數上，懸駝上樓就石磨刀，深為眾人之所嗤笑。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545c02_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "猶如愚人毀破禁戒，多取錢財以用修福望得生天，如懸駝上樓磨刀，用功甚多所得甚少。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545c05_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "19 乘船失釪喻（一九）乘船失釪喻昔有人乘船渡海，失一銀釪墮於水中，即便思念：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545c08_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我今畫水作記，捨之而去後當取之。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545c09_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」行經二月到師子諸國，見一河水，便入其中覓本失釪。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545c10_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸人問言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545c10_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「欲何所作？",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545c11_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」答言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545c11_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我先失釪今欲覓取。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545c11_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」問言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545c11_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「於何處失？",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545c12_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」答言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545c12_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「初入海失。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545c12_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」又復問言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545c12_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「失經幾時？",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545c13_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545c13_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「失來二月。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545c13_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」問言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545c13_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「失來二月，云何此覓？",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545c13_25",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」答言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545c14_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我失釪時畫水作記，本所畫水與此無異，是故覓之。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545c15_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」又復問言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545c15_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「水雖不別，汝昔失時乃在於彼，今在此覓何由可得？",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545c16_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時眾人無不大笑。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545c17_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "亦如外道不修正行，相似善中橫計苦困，以求解脫，猶如愚人失釪於彼而於此覓。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545c19_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "20 人說王縱暴喻（二〇）人說王縱暴喻昔有一人說王過罪，而作是言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545c21_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「王甚暴虐治政無理。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545c22_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」王聞是語即大瞋恚，竟不究悉誰作此語，信傍佞人捉一賢臣，仰使剝脊取百兩肉。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545c24_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有人證明此無是語，王心便悔，索千兩肉用為補脊，夜中呻喚甚大苦惱。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545c26_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "王聞其聲，問言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545c26_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「何以苦惱？",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545c26_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "取汝百兩，十倍與汝，意不足耶？",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545c27_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何故苦惱？",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545c27_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」傍人答言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545c28_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「大王！",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545c28_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如截子頭，雖得千頭不免子死，雖十倍得肉，不免苦痛。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0545c29_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」愚人亦爾，不畏後世貪渴現樂，苦切眾生，調發百姓多得財物，望得滅罪而得福報。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546a02_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如彼王割人之脊取人之肉，以餘肉補望使不痛，無有是處。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546a04_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "21 婦女欲更求子喻（二一）婦女欲更求子喻往昔世時有婦女人，始有一子更欲求子，問餘婦女：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546a07_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「誰有能使我重有子？",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546a07_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」有一老母語此婦言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546a08_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我能使爾求子可得，當須祀天。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546a09_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」問老母言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546a09_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「祀須何物？",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546a09_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」老母語言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546a09_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「殺汝之子取血祀天，必得多子。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546a10_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」時此婦女便隨彼語欲殺其子。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546a11_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "傍有智人嗤笑罵詈：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546a11_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「愚癡無智乃至如此。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546a12_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "未生子者竟可得不？",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546a12_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而殺現子。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546a13_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」愚人亦爾，為未生樂自投火坑，種種害身為得生天。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546a14_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "百喻經卷第一聞如是：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546a16_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一時佛在王舍城，在鵲封竹園，與諸大比丘菩薩摩訶薩及諸八部三萬六千人俱。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546a18_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是時會中有異學梵志五百人俱，從座而起白佛言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546a19_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「吾聞佛道洪深，無能及者，故來歸問，唯願說之。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546a20_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546a20_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「甚善。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546a20_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」問曰：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546a20_23",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「天下為有為無？",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546a21_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」答曰：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546a21_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「亦有亦無。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546a21_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」梵志曰：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546a21_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如今有者，云何言無？",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546a22_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如今無者，云何言有？",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546a22_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」答曰：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546a23_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「生者言有，死者言無，故說或有或無。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546a23_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」問曰：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546a24_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「人從何生？",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546a24_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」答曰：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546a24_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「人從穀而生。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546a24_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」問曰：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546a24_23",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「五穀從何而生？",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546a25_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」答曰：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546a25_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「五穀從四大火風而生。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546a26_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」問曰：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546a26_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「四大火風從何而生？",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546a26_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」答曰：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546a26_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「四大火風從空而生。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546a27_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」問曰：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546a27_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「空從何生？",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546a27_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」答曰：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546a27_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「從無所有生。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546a28_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」問曰：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546a28_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「無所有從何而生？",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546a28_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」答曰：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546a28_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「從自然生。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546a29_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」問曰：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546a29_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「自然從何而生？",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546a29_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」答曰：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546a29_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「從泥洹而生。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546b01_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」問曰：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546b01_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「泥洹從何而生？",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546b01_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546b01_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝今問事何以爾深？",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546b02_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "泥洹者是不生不死法。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546b02_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」問曰：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546b03_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「佛泥洹未？",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546b03_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」答曰：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546b03_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我未泥洹。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546b03_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」「若未泥洹，云何得知泥洹常樂？",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546b04_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546b04_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我今問汝，天下眾生為苦為樂？",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546b05_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」答曰：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546b05_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「眾生甚苦。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546b05_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546b05_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「云何名苦？",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546b06_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」答曰：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546b06_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我見眾生死時苦痛難忍，故知死苦。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546b07_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546b07_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝今不死亦知死苦，我見十方諸佛不生不死故知泥洹常樂。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546b08_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」五百梵志心開意解，求受五戒，悟須陀洹果，復坐如故。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546b10_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546b10_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝等善聽！",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546b10_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "今為汝廣說眾喻。",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546b11_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」",
        "from": "T04n0209_001:0546b11_100",
        "context_with_next_sentence": false
    }
]